{"type":null,"faqId":38983,"title":"为什么我的手环睡眠统计数据不准？","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'\"> </p>\n<div class=\"detail_c_1 fl mt1\">\n<div style=\"POSITION: relative; PADDING-LEFT: 5%; PADDING-RIGHT: 5%\" id=\"softwareDescription\" class=\"column fl\" jQuery17106107134366580053=\"16\">\n<p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', 'serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑', 'sans-serif'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">手环睡眠统计借鉴</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial', 'sans-serif'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">PSG</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑', 'sans-serif'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">睡眠多导图原理，基于</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial', 'sans-serif'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">Cap Sensor</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑', 'sans-serif'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">佩戴监测，通过睡眠状态下手腕的动作来判断睡眠状态。</span></font></p>\n<p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: -21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 39pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', 'serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">l<span style=\"FONT: 10.5pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑', 'sans-serif'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">如果是睡眠数据丢失。可能是用户睡眠时手腕动作较多，使传感器判断为非睡眠，导致数据丢失。如果午睡时间太短低于</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial', 'sans-serif'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">20</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑', 'sans-serif'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">分钟的话，手环可能监测不到，此时不会记录睡眠数据。</span></font></p>\n<p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: -21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 39pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', 'serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">l<span style=\"FONT: 10.5pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑', 'sans-serif'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">如果是睡眠数据误增。可能是手环处于相对比较安静的状态下，并且出现了与睡眠相似的这种动作幅度，使传感器判断为睡眠状态，导致数据误增。比如说，如果您在看电视、或者玩平板时时候出现了误计睡眠，可能是您的动作幅度和频率比较小，和睡觉时的场景比较相似。</span></font></p>\n<p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', 'serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑', 'sans-serif'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">建议在睡眠时可以将手环佩戴在非惯用手上，</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑', 'sans-serif'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\"><font style=\"COLOR: #000000\">目</font>前研发团队正在优化睡眠算法，后续会逐步改善。</span></font></p>\n</div>\n<!--\n<div id=\"floatDiv\"></div>\n--></div>\n</span>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4293","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441673017000,"seriesProductName":"B0-Honor","visitedTimes":53,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}